    "name": {
      "zh": "NKVD 芬卡工具刀",
      "en": "NKVD Finka knife"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "芬卡",
      "en": "Finka"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "由诺文斯克地区著名刀匠打造的复刻版苏联战斗刀；正如其名称所示，“芬卡”融合了芬兰与瑞典刀具的特点。其最初是作为通用工具刀而设计的，在必要时也可用作匕首进行战斗。“芬卡”素以简洁可靠闻名，其刀柄设计带来了舒适稳固的握持感。如今，它更多是作为收藏品，不再实际用作武器。",
      "en": "A replica of the Soviet combat knife crafted by Norvinsk masters, based on Finnish and Swedish designs. Originally used as a utility tool and, when necessary, in combat, the Finka earned a reputation for simplicity and reliability. Its design provides a comfortable, secure grip. Today, it serves more as a collectible piece than a practical weapon."
    },
